{"type":"message","id":"6f0cb24b","parentId":"8fda25e8","timestamp":"2026-03-02T01:59:36.450Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          Based on the skills I can see already installed, here are some of the most useful ones that would be great to have:\n\n## 🔧 已安装的实用技能：\n\n**通信类：**\n- **bluebubbles** - iMessage 集成\n- **discord** - Discord 消息控制\n- **slack** - Slack 集成\n- **imsg** - iMessage/SMS CLI\n\n**生产力工具：**\n- **1password** - 密码管理\n- **notion** - Notion API 集成\n- **obsidian** - Obsidian 笔记管理\n- **github** - GitHub 操作和 PR 管理\n- **gh-issues** - GitHub issue 自动处理\n\n**多媒体处理：**\n- **openai-image-gen** - OpenAI 图像生成\n- **openai-whisper-api** - 语音转文字\n- **video-frames** - 视频帧提取\n- **summarize** - 内容摘要生成\n\n**智能家居/设备控制：**\n- **openhue** - Philips Hue 灯光控制\n- **sonoscli** - Sonos 音箱控制\n- **eightctl** - Eight Sleep 床垫控制\n\n**实用工具：**\n- **weather** - 天气预报\n- **healthcheck** - 系统安全检查\n- **coding-agent** - 代码助手\n- **skill-creator** - 技能创建工具\n\n这些技能已经安装好了，可以直接使用！你想先试试哪个？比如我可以帮你设置天气查询、管理密码、或者控制智能设备？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"ds-v3","model":"ds-v3","usage":{"input":18501,"output":331,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18832,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772416758431}}
